  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "`facetFilters` is a raw Algolia REST API entry while instantsearch.js and the helper are UI abstractions on top of Algolia so we learn the hard way on the various needs of our users like having a fixed facet filter.\n\nIf you are transitioning from JS client + helper to instantsearch.js I would love to have more of your issues. Everytime you hit the feature wall (you are not able to easily do what you want), please open an issue for us to discuss it and make instantsearch.js better.\n",
    "created_at": "2016-06-10T09:53:04Z",
